# NOT src-tauri/gen/ wholesale: gen/android is a real native Android Studio project
# with hand-maintained source (MainActivity.kt's share-target ingest + ShareBridge,
# AndroidManifest.xml's SEND intent-filter + FileProvider, res/xml/file_paths.xml) —
# Tauri's own convention is to commit gen/android (see its OWN nested .gitignore at
# src-tauri/gen/android/.gitignore, which already excludes just the Gradle/IDE build
# noise: build/, .gradle, .idea/*, local.properties, keystores). Blanket-ignoring the
# parent dir here shadowed that and left the hand-edits untracked with no way to
# survive a fresh clone. gen/schemas/ (ACL/capability schemas) stays ignored — pure
# regenerated output, never hand-edited.
src-tauri/gen/schemas/
